divs: sighting detailsoutside smoking cigarette on friday evening i was watching two planes\jets flying south to north, when a bright white pulsating light suddenly appeared and shot from west to east. at first i thought it was a shooting star but it didn't burn out. the light continued east leaving no contrail and disaapeared in about 45 seconds. i feel this could not have been a plane or jet because there were a few planes\jets in the area and i could clearly see the differnce between those and this object. this object was moving much faster than anything i have ever observed in the sky short of a shooting star or shuttle\rocket launch and made no sound.
Summary: pulsating light going west to east very fast
